OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew rail strikes ballot to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstart soon - RMT boss      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rail workers will be balloted "soon" on
OL,6, whether to stage fresh strikes later in
OL,7, the year, the RMT union's general      
OL,8, secretary Mick Lynch has said.         
OL,10,FMr Lynch told the BBC the union wanted 
OL,11,Fto "keep talking" about pay, but felt  
OL,12,Fthe government was "trying to make an  
OL,13,Fexample out of the railways".          
OL,15,FOn Friday, the union rejected what was 
OL,16,Fdescribed as a "best and final" offer  
OL,17,Ffrom the body representing rail firms. 
OL,19,FThe government and Network Rail have   
OL,20,Fcondemned the decision.                
